---
title: Chorizo Crumbed Leek and Potato Soup with warm brioche bread
description: Leek and potato soup is a classically Irish recipe that's creamy, comforting, and wonderfully warming. This particular dish is spiced up just a bit with the addition of a herby and smoky chorizo crumb.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221004_R04_W47_IE_IECFP0159-1_MB_Main_High-d946204d.jpg
